title: Skating In The Park
description:
Our story tonight is called “Skating in the Park” and it’s a story about revisiting a yearly tradition. It’s also about a thermos of coffee waiting to warm you up, thick socks and the kind of friends who even after a while apart, can pick right back up where they left off.

So get cozy and ready to sleep.

Order the book now! hyperurl.co/NothingMuchHappens
